# NOTE: See BB’s notes on readings. The use of ascetics for spies is recommended by the Aryhasastra, and is still alive and well today, being a standard technique under Communism.
#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "sn3.11:7.1"
msgid "Ete, bhante, mama purisā carā ocarakā janapadaṃ ocaritvā āgacchanti. "
msgstr "Sir, these are my spies, my undercover agents returning after spying on the country. "

#. VAR: osāpayissāmi → oyāyissāmi (bj) | ohayissāmi (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "sn3.11:7.2"
msgid "Tehi paṭhamaṃ ociṇṇaṃ ahaṃ pacchā osāpayissāmi. "
msgstr "First they go undercover, then I have them report to me. "

#. VAR: odātavatthā → odātavatthavasanā (bj, s1-3, pts2)
msgctxt "sn3.11:7.3"
msgid "Idāni te, bhante, taṃ rajojallaṃ pavāhetvā sunhātā suvilittā kappitakesamassū odātavatthā pañcahi kāmaguṇehi samappitā samaṅgībhūtā paricāressantī”ti. "
msgstr "And now—when they have washed off the dust and dirt, and are nicely bathed and anointed, with hair and beard dressed, and dressed in white—they will amuse themselves, supplied and provided with the five kinds of sensual stimulation.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc8
msgctxt "sn3.11:8.1"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā etamatthaṃ viditvā tāyaṃ velāyaṃ imā gāthāyo abhāsi: "
msgstr "Then, knowing the meaning of this, on that occasion the Buddha recited these verses: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.181, sc9
msgctxt "sn3.11:9.1"
msgid "“Na vaṇṇarūpena naro sujāno, "
msgstr "“It’s not easy to know a man by his appearance. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn3.11:9.2"
msgid "Na vissase ittaradassanena; "
msgstr "You shouldn’t trust them at first sight. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn3.11:9.3"
msgid "Susaññatānañhi viyañjanena, "
msgstr "For undisciplined men live in this world "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn3.11:9.4"
msgid "Asaññatā lokamimaṃ caranti. "
msgstr "disguised as the disciplined. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc10
msgctxt "sn3.11:10.1"
msgid "Patirūpako mattikākuṇḍalova, "
msgstr "Like a fake earring made of clay, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn3.11:10.2"
msgid "Lohaḍḍhamāsova suvaṇṇachanno; "
msgstr "like a copper halfpenny coated with gold, "

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: loke → eke (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "sn3.11:10.3"
msgid "Caranti loke parivārachannā, "
msgstr "they live hidden in the world, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn3.11:10.4"
msgid "Anto asuddhā bahi sobhamānā”ti. "
msgstr "corrupt inside but impressive outside.”"

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
